text.tspan: At Wasatch Music, we believe in the importance
of supporting local musicians. We are commited
to helping Utahns find fantastic new music
created by fellow Utahns. All of our featured
artists are local, and we curate playlists based off
their sound and their musical inspirations. These
playlists include music from all over the world,
but they are always based on local bands.
Upcoming shows are updated weekly. If you
miss a show, you can read all about it
